{"tid":1718162,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"由612到今日 唔該全部手足同我入一入黎","createTime":"2019-11-13T19:09:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T03:56:39.000Z","uid":89676,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"93476378ac47eed4c48b6ba025f42de64946064d","tid":1718162,"uid":89676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T19:09:26.000Z","msg":"由612開始觀察到今日 希望可以比小小意見<br />\n<br />\n極度建議前線手足開花果陣一人袋一支噴漆係身<br />\n<br />\n1.重量唔係好重唔會影響比狗追果彈既速度<br />\n<br />\n2.前線手足比人拉左返去救人可以噴落去啲狗既頭盔<br />\n   遮住啲狗既視線 救人同時保護埋自己安全 方便走人<br />\n<br />\n3.佢地頭盔必需更換 可以消耗佢地裝備<br />\n<br />\n4.噴漆可以由物資手足準備 亦可以隨時係街作文宣<br />\n<br />\n5.百利而無一害 做左先<br />\n<br />\n當2至3個人一齊救手足可以成功率更高<br />\n光復香港 一個都不能少<br />\n<br />\n各位手足<br />\n武運昌隆 時代革命"},{"pid":"f82ed0a6a3cabce10858e7c8f8233aa5cb6280f2","tid":1718162,"uid":303090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T19:11:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a3cc412f96f0ed46ac11c2b921cd82c70488994","tid":1718162,"uid":89676,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T19:12:11.000Z","msg":"唔想再有人死 推一推"},{"pid":"418fcee13d6f08dcde936941360ce485d63ff61d","tid":1718162,"uid":89676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T19:16:31.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df22147b7f1222a1cf546c122f4e89e545cd977","tid":1718162,"uid":89676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T19:22:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"960766b14f4729000c00dd3b2cee35da7c906c5e","tid":1718162,"uid":89676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T19:26:27.000Z","msg":"推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"205082df4be0648b4a4b60ecd16961f8e40189eb","tid":1718162,"uid":12354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T19:29:45.000Z","msg":"呢個幾可行"},{"pid":"687f31614ae2275eb552be87e4bf1aeedc9ca6ca","tid":1718162,"uid":74028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"